434
00:31:23,410 --> 00:31:27,060
I just told you you're being haunted by the ghost of your wife, and you...

435
00:31:27,060 --> 00:31:30,230
Neil, I need to have a serious conversation with you.

436
00:31:30,230 --> 00:31:33,050
You were having an affair... Tell him something I wouldn't know.

437
00:31:33,050 --> 00:31:35,700
I've got a feather tattooed on my arse.

438
00:31:39,090 --> 00:31:41,010
She's got a feather on her bum.

439
00:31:41,010 --> 00:31:43,920
Something you'd also know if you'd slept with her.

440
00:31:43,920 --> 00:31:46,290
He called me Squidge for three months after we first got together

441
00:31:46,290 --> 00:31:49,490
